title: This is the Police - crack incl
description:
Dive into a deep story of corruption crime and intrigue. Take the
role of gritty Police Chief Jack Boyd and come face to face with
the ugly underbelly of Freeburg a city spiraling the drain. Will
Jack reach his retirement with a nice stack of bills or will he
end up broken ... or worse Manage your staff respond to
emergencies and investigate crimes in a city on the brink of
chaos
